## Accessibility Commitment

This software is specifically designed to be accessible to users with disabilities.
We are committed to maintaining and improving accessibility features. If you
encounter any accessibility barriers, please report them as high-priority issues.

## AI Collaboration Notice

This project is developed through collaborative AI systems (Amazon Q, GitHub Copilot, 
Google Gemini) working together under established rules to ensure continuous 
improvement while maintaining accessibility standards.